<section sectnbr = "1F">
<servcat sctnbr = "01" scnbr = "06">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "S5JB0B1606018" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Cooling System Flushing
</title>
<attention1>
<ptxt>
To help avoid danger of being burned, do not remove degassing tank cap while engine and radiator are still hot. Scalding fluid and steam can be blown out under pressure if cap is taken off too soon.
</ptxt>
</attention1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drain coolant referring to 
<intxref refid = "S5JB0B1606004">Cooling System Draining</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Close radiator drain plug.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove air ventilation plug (2) from thermostat assembly (3).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Fill degassing tank with water until water flow out from air ventilation plug, and then tighten air ventilation plug.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Fill degassing tank with coolant up to &#8220;MAXI&#8221; level mark (4).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install degassing tank cap (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5JB0B160004.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "102.309mm" ver = "02" gw = "174" gh = "273"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.245in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
5.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
&#8220;MINI&#8221; level mark
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Run engine until upper radiator hose is hot.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Stop engine.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Wait until engine is cooled, and drain water from cooling system.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Repeat Step 2) to 9) several times until drained liquid is nearly colorless.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Fill cooling system with coolant referring to 
<intxref refid = "S5JB0B1606005">Cooling System Refilling</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfo>
